Validator
public class MockValidator
extends AbstractValidator

Mocked Validator for testing your controllers. You can use the idiom: MockValidator validator = new MockValidator(); MyController controller = new MyController(..., validator); try { controller.method(); Assert.fail(); } catch (ValidationError e) { List errors = e.getErrors(); // asserts } or

Lucas Cavalcanti
